title: Dean Martin - The Very Best Of Dean Martin (1998) musicfromrizzo
description:
Dean Martin - The Very Best Of Dean Martin (The Capitol & Reprise Years) (1998) 320k (musicfromrizzo)

Some truly great Dean Martin greatest hits here including Sway, Everybody loves somebody In the chapel in the moonlight, Thats amore - and lots more of the same sort of great hits! I've included a bonus song - one of my favourite songs I only discovered years ago was also done by Dean - You are always in my heart!

enjoy and thanks for seeding!

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
